# add_irida_user_to_project
# add a user to an IRIDA project
# any authenticated user who is a member of the project can add users
#
# usage: add_irida_user_to_project USERNAME PROJECT_ID ROLE [METADATA_ROLE]
#
# ROLE:          PROJECT_USER (Collaborator) or PROJECT_OWNER (Manager)
# METADATA_ROLE: LEVEL_1 through LEVEL_4 (optional, defaults to LEVEL_1)
#
# NOTE: IRIDA does not validate the role field - invalid values are silently
#       accepted and default to PROJECT_USER / LEVEL_1
# NOTE: any authenticated user who is a member of the project can add any
#       system user to the project via the API. The web UI restricts this
#       to project managers only. This is an RBAC gap.
#
# example: add_irida_user_to_project rakuip:Raoul_Valentin_Kuiper 150:test_gmarselis PROJECT_USER LEVEL_1
